                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Other Resources</td>
                    <td>CDs/ DVDs</td>
                    <td>3750</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="membership-details">
    <div class="membership-details-wrapper reveal">
        <div class="membership-details-header">
            <h1>MEMBERSHIP DETAILS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="membership-details-text">
            <p>The Library has an impressive collection of Standard & University prescribed text and reference books. Based on student needs & faculty recommendation, multiple copies of text books are bought and made available.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="membership-details-table-container">
            <table class="membership-details-table">
